            "rationale": "Every other deferred decision in the ROADMAP carries an OED-3xx label (OED-301 through OED-305). The 'Conformance fixture set' entry in Phase 1 Decisions Deferred ('The exact set of canonical-v0.4 fixtures (\u00c2\u00a721.3) must be agreed before goldens are committed') is an informal entry with no machine-referenceable identifier. Downstream artifacts \u00e2\u20ac\u201d synthesist documents, developer change proposals, Barcode audit history \u00e2\u20ac\u201d cross-reference decisions by OED identifier; without one, this decision cannot be reliably tracked, closed, or audited. The critic confirmed without material extension. The source artifact confirms the unidentified entry at line 55.",
