          "STEP 9: Estimate your output size before emitting. If the changes[] payload would exceed approximately 20,000 characters total, emit fewer changes (consolidate adjacent ones into larger before/after pairs). The substrate's LLM dispatch has a hard ceiling at 32,000 output tokens per turn; staying under 20,000 characters of changes[] content keeps headroom."
        ],
