        "open_questions": [
          "Does `projectSemantic()` belong in `src/kernel/` (alongside `canonicalize.ts` and `transform.ts`) or in a new module? The IMPLEMENTATION_PLAN does not specify the file location.",
          "Is `ecm:name` retained or stripped in the semantic projection output? SPEC \u00c2\u00a76.1 predicate allowlist omits it; SPEC \u00c2\u00a76.2 prose names it as a Semantic Layer field on the project root (SPEC.md:722). A strict-allowlist implementation strips it; \u00c2\u00a76.2 prose implies it should be retained.",
          "Does `fast-check` need Human Orchestrator approval before the AC3 property-based test can be implemented? Alternatively, is a hand-rolled \u00e2\u2030\u00a550-iteration loop (as precedent from existing test files) acceptable for the 'property-based' label in AC3?",
          "Does the TBox-in-@graph ambiguity (SPEC \u00c2\u00a76.3 step 5 'Prepend' vs \u00c2\u00a731 '@graph' node-objects) apply to the `projectSemantic()` return value, or only to the downstream semantic-JSON-LD emitter (task 1.5)? The steps are 1\u00e2\u20ac\u201c6 in \u00c2\u00a76.3, step 5 being TBox prepend \u00e2\u20ac\u201d task 1.4 implements all six steps.",
          "Should `rdfs:domain` and `rdfs:range` compact IRIs in TBox node-objects from `getProjectTBoxNodes()` be expanded in the `projectSemantic()` output, and if so, does VMP_CONTEXT need to be supplemented (per the note at `src/tbox/index.ts:74-76`)?"
