        "open_questions": [
          "Does refactorIri also update the id field of the entity being renamed (e.g., the term or instance whose IRI is oldIri), or does it only update the four reference field types? IMPLEMENTATION_PLAN \u00c2\u00a71.7 sub-tasks list only the four reference fields; AC1 does not check entity id fields; but SPEC \u00c2\u00a713.2/\u00c2\u00a713.4 describe a complete identity change. The developer and architect must decide the scope.",
