        "open_questions": [
          "The severity taxonomy contradiction (LEGACY_REALIST_ANCHOR_PLACEHOLDER is \u00c2\u00a717.1 'info' yet blocks export per \u00c2\u00a717.4) has no ADR resolution. Should the implementation treat export-blocking as a special per-finding attribute rather than inferring it from severity level? This affects how the CLI and UI interpret the findings array.",
          "SPEC \u00c2\u00a710.5 Snapshot Migration is cited in IMPL PLAN \u00c2\u00a71.9 SPEC refs but AC1\u00e2\u20ac\u201cAC5 do not include any snapshot-migration test case. Is snapshot migration in scope for task 1.9 or deferred?",
          "FR-C013 covers only v0.2\u00e2\u2020\u2019v0.3; the v0.3\u00e2\u2020\u2019v0.4 leg has no FR-C identifier (gap F3 from prior spec review). Should a new FR-C be added to SPEC.md to complete the requirements coverage, or is the IMPL PLAN \u00c2\u00a71.9 reference sufficient?",
