            "claim": "Tests follow a hand-rolled pattern: no test framework (no Vitest/Jest yet), using `node:assert`, `process.exit(1)` on failure, discovered by `tests/run-tests.ts` which scans for `*.test.js` files and runs each in a separate child process.",
