        "dep_classification_default": "Per OPERATOR-MEDIATION-LOG Event 3: browser-app convention. Add ALL of these to devDependencies (NOT dependencies): react ^18, react-dom ^18, @types/react ^18, @types/react-dom ^18, vite ^5, @vitejs/plugin-react ^4, @playwright/test ^1. No 'dependencies' field additions required; bundle is the artifact.",
        "scope_warning_token_limit": "LARGE substantive scope (new build tooling + 4 layout panels + 3 file I/O flows + Playwright suite). Estimate output BEFORE emitting changes[]: if >20000 chars, propose scope-split via self_assessment. Suggested scope-split: Chain 1 = Vite config + package.json devDeps + src/ui/App.tsx with empty 4-panel layout + tsconfig adjustments + simple Playwright smoke test (AC1: loads in Chromium). Chains 2+ add New/Open/Save (AC2-AC4) + migration notice (AC5).",
