        "open_questions": [
          "Is the test/fixtures/canonical-v0.4/minimal.jsonld fixture byte-identical to the serializeVmp() output for the same data? (normalizeOnLoad would mutate it before Save if not; AC3 'bytewise identical' assertion depends on this.) This requires running the code to determine.",
