          "Should the Blob-download Save mechanism live directly in src/ui/App.tsx (inline anchor-click pattern) or in a new src/adapters/persistence/ module, given that SPEC \u00c2\u00a74.1.2 classifies browser download/upload as an adapter? Chain 2 developer needs an architectural ruling.",
