            "id": "F5",
            "claim": "`refactorIri` does NOT update entity `id` fields; it updates only the four reference field types (`ecm:classIris`, `ecm:predicateIri`, `ecm:subjectIri`, `ecm:objectIri`); this is a known open question (F9) from prior reconnaissance task `urn:fnsr:task:123-recon-iri-refactor`.",
            "evidence": [
