            "describe": "Chain C: AC4 (load fixture with ecm:imported-ontology term \u00e2\u2020\u2019 no edit affordance visible or interactable for that term: gw-btn-add-class exists but imported term row has no click handler opening an edit dialog; aria-disabled or absence of data-testid confirms read-only state)."
          },
          {
