            "id": "F4",
            "claim": "`TermSection` (inside TermSidebar.tsx) renders each term as a `<li>` element with no `onClick` handler on the item; there is no per-term click callback prop in `TermSection` or `TermSidebar`.",
            "evidence": [
              {
