      "inputs": {
        "task_context": "Phase 2 task 2.3 Chain B: Edit project-created term (FR-U009) + Refactor-IRI confirmation dialog. Builds on Chain A's Dialog.tsx + AddTermDialog.tsx + TermSidebar updates. Chain B covers AC2 (Edit class label -> Save -> rdfs:label updated) and AC3 (Edit class IRI: confirmation dialog with affected reference count).",
        "output_envelope_constraint": "Output wrapped: outputs.findings[] (array of {id, claim, evidence, kind}), outputs.summary, outputs.evidence_paths.",
        "goal": "Read-only investigation for Phase 2 task 2.3 Chain B. Focus: identify Chain A's Dialog.tsx component interface (reuse for EditTermDialog + Refactor-IRI confirm); identify src/refactor/ interface for getting affected-reference count without applying; identify rdfs:comment handling in term schema.",
        "focus_areas": [
