        "summary": "10 changes across 4 files (2 new, 2 edited). C1 creates EditTermDialog.tsx with a two-phase flow (edit form \u00e2\u2020\u2019 refactor confirmation) that reuses Dialog from Chain A and calls refactorIri() as a pure-function count source. C2-C7 extend TermSidebar.tsx: EditTermDialog import, rdfs:comment on TermEntry, onTermClick prop on TermSection (conditional on ecm:source=project-created), editTerm state + handleEditConfirm handler, updated return block wiring. C8 creates a cross-reference fixture (Person class + one classifying instance) for AC3. C9-C10 extend term-crud.spec.ts with the CROSS_REFS_FIXTURE constant and two new tests: AC2 (label edit round-trip via save/parse) and AC3 (IRI change \u00e2\u2020\u2019 confirmation dialog with count > 0). App.tsx requires no change: the existing onTermsChange prop already covers the state update path.",
