        "open_questions": [
          "When `ecm:layouts` contains multiple ecm:CanvasLayout entries, which is the 'active' layout? SPEC \u00c2\u00a75.11 defines the object shape but does not specify layout selection policy (first, named 'Default Layout', most recent, or a project-settings pointer).",
          "Does Chain A need to auto-generate a CanvasLayout entry (with default positions) when a project has ecm:instances but an empty ecm:layouts array? The developer task says 'derive React Flow nodes from ecm:instances (mapping ecm:CanvasNode position if present, else auto-layout)' \u00e2\u20ac\u201d the 'else auto-layout' path implies a write-back to ecm:layouts, but Chain A is described as read-only.",
