        "implementation_directions": [
          "CanvasView.tsx edit: enable React Flow edge creation via onConnect handler (FR-U014). On connect: generate new IRI; construct ecm:RelationAssertion with subjectIri=source-node's-instance-IRI, objectIri=target-node's-instance-IRI, predicateIri=null OR default (per SPEC); append to ecm:relations array; setProject.",
          "Enable edge selection: React Flow onEdgesChange or onSelectionChange to track currently-selected edge. Pass selected-edge-id up to App.tsx state.",
          "Inspector.tsx: new component in src/ui/ rendered in right sidebar. Takes selected entity (relation, in this chain) as prop. For a selected relation: shows subjectIri (read-only label of source instance), predicate dropdown populated with all owl:ObjectProperty terms in the project (FR-U015), objectIri (read-only label of target instance), 'Reverse' button (FR-U016: swap subject/object), 'Delete' button (FR-U017: remove relation).",
          "App.tsx: replace right-sidebar placeholder with <Inspector selectedRelation={...} project={project} setProject={setProject} />; track selectedRelationId from CanvasView.",
          "Tests: tests/playwright/relation-crud.spec.ts with 4 tests (AC1-AC4). Reuse canvas fixture or create a 2-instance + 1-OP-term fixture suitable for these tests. AC1: drag from one node to another; save; parse; assert new ecm:relations entry. AC2: select existing relation; pick predicate from dropdown; save; parse; assert ecm:predicateIri updated. AC3: select; click Reverse; save; parse; assert subjectIri/objectIri swapped. AC4: select; click Delete; save; parse; assert relation absent from ecm:relations."
        ],
