            "claim": "SPEC \u00c2\u00a75.10 defines the full ecm:LiteralAssertion schema with seven required/optional fields: id, type, ecm:subjectIri, ecm:predicateIri, ecm:value, ecm:datatype (required), and ecm:language (optional, null-able).",
