        "goal": "Propose changes[] implementing Chain A scope only: onNodeSelect wiring + selectedInstanceId state + Inspector instance-mode + AddLiteralDialog + Delete handler in Inspector + AC1+AC2+AC3 Playwright tests. AC1 = Add literal; AC2 = Add with language='en'; AC3 = Delete. Edit (FR-U019 edit half) deferred to follow-up chain; no AC binding.",
