        "task_context": "Phase 2 task 2.9: iao:isAbout Declaration UI (SPEC \u00a75.4.1, \u00a717.2, FR-U031, NFR-014). 4 ACs covering MISSING_REALIST_ANCHOR indicator + add subject IRI + indicator-absence after declaration + LEGACY_REALIST_ANCHOR_PLACEHOLDER indicator.",
