        "implementation_directions": [
          "Add a header indicator banner that shows MISSING_REALIST_ANCHOR or LEGACY_REALIST_ANCHOR_PLACEHOLDER state. Detection: MISSING = iao:isAbout is empty/absent; LEGACY = iao:isAbout contains the placeholder IRI (per recon findings). Both indicators have a 'Set real subject' / 'Add subject IRI' affordance that opens the project-settings dialog.",
          "ProjectSettingsDialog.tsx: new component with iao:isAbout list (each entry: IRI display + Remove button) + 'Add IRI' input + Save button. On Add: validate IRI shape (not empty, not the legacy placeholder if MISSING-mode); append to iao:isAbout; setProject. On Remove: filter out; setProject.",
