            "content": "The chain-A / chain-B / chain-C split \u00e2\u20ac\u201d implement the unblocking UI in Chain A, add targeted Playwright tests in Chain B, integrate into the smoke suite in Chain C \u00e2\u20ac\u201d provides a clean dependency ordering that allows smoke-suite work (task 2.12) to unblock incrementally as each UI gap closes. The ratification scope was explicitly bounded to 'single file edit; no test additions' with tests deferred to Chain B/C, making the chain-boundary the natural ratification scope boundary as well. This pattern is worth formalizing for future Phase 2 gap-closure work where the UI change is the prerequisite and the test suite is the downstream deliverable."
